    { "message_id": "om_001", "sender": "ou_pm_lin", "create_time": "2026-04-21T10:02:00+08:00", "msg_type": "text", "content": "@all 早，周会开始。本周目标：完成 cache 层 + 数据看板 v1 上线。今天先把缓存方案定了。" },
    { "message_id": "om_002", "sender": "ou_yl_alex", "create_time": "2026-04-21T10:03:00+08:00", "msg_type": "text", "content": "我倾向 Memcached，benchmark 上 read latency 比 Redis 低 30%。" },
    { "message_id": "om_003", "sender": "ou_chen_xb", "create_time": "2026-04-21T10:04:30+08:00", "msg_type": "text", "content": "Redis 吧，团队已经有运维经验，且我们后面需要持久化能力。Memcached 上线还得搭一套监控。" },
    { "message_id": "om_004", "sender": "ou_yl_alex", "create_time": "2026-04-21T10:05:10+08:00", "msg_type": "text", "content": "持久化我们用得上吗？看板数据本来就能从主库重建。" },
    { "message_id": "om_005", "sender": "ou_pm_lin", "create_time": "2026-04-21T10:06:00+08:00", "msg_type": "text", "content": "先搁置，我中午想想。@小陈 你下午把两边的数据再整理一下" },
    { "message_id": "om_006", "sender": "ou_chen_xb", "create_time": "2026-04-21T10:06:20+08:00", "msg_type": "text", "content": "好的，下午前给。" },
    { "message_id": "om_007", "sender": "ou_pm_lin", "create_time": "2026-04-21T10:07:00+08:00", "msg_type": "text", "content": "另外周报规则定一下：每周五下午 5 点前在群里发，标题统一格式：周报-Omega-Wxx。这是硬规定。" },
